findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function distributeRewards() uses the native token balance to calculate reward in FREE token which may cause the function to not work properly due to big decimal difference.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges when they have not renounced ownership, including minting tokens and calling the distributeRewards() function.
